aph","text":"5、分配：积累与消费问题","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"6d666509cb","type":"paragraph","text":"6、普遍推行试验田","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"b3a9521a07","type":"paragraph","text":"7、红与专、政治与业务(技术)的对立统一，一定要批判不问政治的错误倾向，反对空头政治家(名红实白)和迷失方向的经济家这样两种人","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"43f254d18d","type":"paragraph","text":"8、整风一定要坚持到底，全党提起干劲，打掉官风，实事求是，与人民打成一片，肃清一切作风上、工作上、制度上的错误。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"d7c6bdbf18","type":"paragraph","text":"9、在整风中每单位以几天工夫来一次反浪费的鸣放整改，干部的；每个家庭的。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"261e1351b9","type":"paragraph","text":"10、何时交计划?(六月?)省的，地的，县的，社的。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"37732b208f","type":"paragraph","text":"11、开展以除四害为中心〔的〕伟大爱国卫生运动。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"c6473eef79","type":"paragraph","text":"12、夏季为什么不能种树?","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"e9eb7e779d","type":"paragraph","text":"13、省一年开中小型会议四次，几十人的，百多人的，二三百人的，检查工作，发现问题，解决问题。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"1730176024","type":"paragraph","text":"14、书记、委员大多数人，轮番离开办公室，一年一定要有四个月，到处跑，走马看花，下马看花。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"fbb7d185f8","type":"paragraph","text":"15、地方工业超过农业要多少时间，五年?十年?要做一个计划。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"a0dc88af8b","type":"paragraph","text":"16、不断革命论","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"84f2220a3a","type":"paragraph","text":"夺取政权——土地革命(民主主义的)——再一次土地革命(社会主义的)——社会主义的思想的政治的革命——技术革命","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"a822e19cd0","type":"paragraph","text":"从1958起，在继续完成思想、政治革命的同时，着重点应放技术革命方面。当然是经济与政治、技术与政治的统一，年年如此。思想、政治是统帅，是君，技术是士兵，是臣，思想政治又是技术的保证。","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"8340f0dc4c","type":"paragraph","text":"阶级消灭以后，人与人之间的思想政治斗争，或革命，继续进行，但性质变了。国家权力，在对内职能上，逐逐<步>地不存在了，现在对劳动人〔民〕也已基本不存〔在〕了——说服而非压服，打倒官气，十分必要。","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"090c6986ee","type":"paragraph","text":"政治家，一定要懂一些业务，在农业是试验田，在工业试制产品，两者都用比较法，在同一条件下，先进与落后比较。企业与企业比，车间与车间比，个人与〔个〕人比。","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"c1d1c7a469","type":"paragraph","text":"技术方面比，政治方面也要比，看谁领导得更好","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"74acd96d52","type":"paragraph","text":"不平衡——平衡——再一个不平衡——再一个平衡以至无穷，这就是规律","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"7140434476","type":"paragraph","text":"上层建筑是为基础服务的，政治权力和意识形态(即思想)是为经济服务的","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"437eae9d8e","type":"paragraph","text":"17、文件的准确性，鲜明性，生动性","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"cce640326d","type":"paragraph","text":"古代考据学，要解决的问题，是概念和判断的问题，公式是什么是什么。","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"1233ca4279","type":"paragraph","text":"例如：皇考是远祖，还是祖父，还是父亲?三后是楚国的三后，还是禹、汤、文，还是颛顼、帝俈、轩辕?兰是现在这样的兰，还是另外一种?","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"ced4daa35f","type":"paragraph","text":"以上是概念问题。","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"8aa52916ea","type":"paragraph","text":"例如：昔三后之纯粹兮，固众〔芳〕之所在。〔彼〕尧舜之耿介兮，固<既>遵道而得路；何桀纣之昌<猖>披兮，夫唯截<捷>径以准<窘)步?","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"c6f0f40240","type":"paragraph","text":"以上，是判断问题。","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"9fb99fa04e","type":"paragraph","text":"古代的义理学，要解决〔的〕问题，是推理的问题","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"a58d45003b","type":"paragraph","text":"以上二学，都属理性认识。","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"17a9ac8629","type":"paragraph","text":"18、抓两头，带中间。一个好的方法。","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"cf1442331d","type":"paragraph","text":"19、五年看三年，三年看头年。是一个真理，也是方法。","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"e2a2c2d910","type":"paragraph","text":"20、一年检查四次，每季一次。非常会议一次至两次。一种好的方法。中央、省、地三级，都这样做。今年试一试这个方法。","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"23747871f3","type":"paragraph","text":"中央、省、地三级的委员每年要有四个月时间离开办公室，到处跑，走马，下马。","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"677e525f44","type":"subtitle","text":"二","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"be5c334c19","type":"paragraph","text":"这肯定是一个好方法。","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"271cf62a71","type":"paragraph","text":"今年实行。","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"58fb52f041","type":"paragraph","text":"少一天也不可以。","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"3f0086216c","type":"paragraph","text":"开会的方法：材料与观点的统一。","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"173b49dbc1","type":"paragraph","text":"用材料去说明自己的观点(思想，意见)。将两者割断，互不联系，是一个很坏方法，并且不生动，使人头痛。","index":45,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"93d8e42fac","type":"paragraph","text":"有材料，无观点，则更坏。","index":46,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"edc4e899cd","type":"paragraph","text":"只需要典型性的材料，解剖一个或二三个麻雀就行。一大堆材料，只会使人短命。自己应〔有〕丰丰<富>的材料，但在会议上只需要拿典型。会议所需要使用的材料，和写大著作(例如资本论)所需要使用的材料，有所不同。","index":47,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"3454379fd1","type":"paragraph","text":"九个指头与一个指头的区别","index":48,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"a1ea21ead0","type":"paragraph","text":"大局与小局的区别","index":49,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"eb6d632216","type":"paragraph","text":"一般与特殊的区别","index":50,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"36dca00a5b","type":"paragraph","text":"抓住主流。抓错了(抓了支流)，一定裁<栽>筋斗。","index":51,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"e82efb39bc","type":"paragraph","text":"这是现实问题，也是逻辑问题。","index":52,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"8acbdfdcf9","type":"paragraph","text":"“反冒进”的教训：反掉了三个东西，把一些同志抛到〔同〕右派似乎相近的地位。","index":53,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"dd1ed8cdb8","type":"paragraph","text":"“砍掉十万个合作〔社〕”的教训。","index":54,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"8ef05653bd","type":"paragraph","text":"响应反斯大林的教训，完全跟着赫鲁晓夫的指挥棍跑。","index":55,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"0cf0c0e001","type":"paragraph","text":"响应高饶的教训","index":56,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"1bcaf6f224","type":"paragraph","text":"登徒子好色赋的方法","index":57,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"25ee709d78","type":"paragraph","text":"我们同志中采用这种方法的人，很不少。革命吃亏很大。","index":58,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"54f9d0e31c","type":"paragraph","text":"同少数同志交换意见的方法：","index":59,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"635ebd6a68","type":"paragraph","text":"同个别人，同十几人，同二十几人反复交换，多次交换，从而得出比较正确观点、政策。","index":60,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"806e18e363","type":"paragraph","text":"集体创造的方法，是比较可靠的方法。","index":61,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"5fb62a7a43","type":"paragraph","text":"以一个人为核心","index":62,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"515a4fb4a0","type":"paragraph","text":"看报纸和研究报纸，看文件和研究文件的方法：","index":63,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId"