夫错误的材料，吸取苏联的教训。","index":76,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"f3fa9c8837","type":"paragraph","text":"27、学本地话，学普通话。","index":77,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"797aa3f653","type":"paragraph","text":"28、中央和省市两级的主要干部建议在自愿原则上会一国外国文，五年至十年，达到中学程度。","index":78,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"49751f0fc7","type":"paragraph","text":"29、学一点文学。","index":79,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"3a0fd536f8","type":"paragraph","text":"30、学一点文法和逻辑。","index":80,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"bf9b2be33f","type":"paragraph","text":"31、学一点自然科学和技术科学。","index":81,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"b46e751d99","type":"paragraph","text":"32、学一点哲学和政治经济学。","index":82,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"8891bc243c","type":"paragraph","text":"33、学一点历史和法学。","index":83,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"a071af3894","type":"paragraph","text":"考虑当教授和当教员的问题。","index":84,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"44afa2b84e","type":"paragraph","text":"考虑出刊物的问题。","index":85,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"10aec4cd82","type":"paragraph","text":"34、干部和秘书的统一，不可以一切依赖秘书和二排议员。自己动手为主，别人帮助为辅。","index":86,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"478028aa72","type":"paragraph","text":"35、中央一级、省一级的若干主要负责人，可以设置一名学习秘书。","index":87,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"2a90e915c9","type":"paragraph","text":"36、我辞去共和国主席的问题，在今年九月以前用征求各级干部意见的方式举行一次鸣放辩论，然后在工厂、合作社、学校、机关中，凡是有群众的地方，举行辩论，求得多数人同意。","index":88,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f3f198e18c"},{"id":"13d1d9a209","type":"paragraph","text":"37、在三级(或四级?)会议上讨论一次党的领导原则问题。“大权独揽，小权分散，党委决定，各方去办。办也有决，不离原则(党是阶级组织的最高形式，民主集中制，个人作用和集体领导的统一——班长与战士的统一，上级的决议和指示)，工作检查，党委有责。”是否正确?","index":89,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayueji